prerequisite : 
package manager : jspm (npm install jspm -g)
http server : http-server (npm install http-server -g)
task runner : gulp (npm install gulp -g)

On a new empty directory : 

* to configure project for jspm :
jspm init -y

* to add dependencies :
jspm install aurelia-bootstrapper aurelia-fetch-client moment

* config.js customization : 
babelOptions: {
    "optional": [
      "es7.decorators",
      "es7.classProperties"
    ]
  }

paths: {
    "*": "src/*",
    "github:*": "jspm_packages/github/*",
    "npm:*": "jspm_packages/npm/*"
  }

* to start the server :
http-server -p 8090 -c-1

